# ‚úÖ Why stale closures are common in `useEffect` & async handlers

## üîë Core reason (memorize this)

> **Closures capture values at render time, but `useEffect` and async callbacks run later.**

That time gap is what causes bugs.

***

# üßÝ React‚Äôs mental model (important)

Each render creates **a new snapshot of state**.

    Render #1 ‚Üí state = 0
    Render #2 ‚Üí state = 1
    Render #3 ‚Üí state = 2

Functions created in **render #1** permanently ‚Äúremember‚Äù `state = 0`.

