# 7Ô∏è‚É£ Rules you can rely on (very important)

## ‚úÖ Rule 1 ‚Äî Snapshot rule

> State values are **snapshots per render**.

## ‚úÖ Rule 2 ‚Äî Delay rule

> If code runs later, it may use **stale values**.

## ‚úÖ Rule 3 ‚Äî Fix hierarchy

1.  Prefer **functional updates**
2.  Use **dependencies correctly**
3.  Use **refs only when necessary**

